{"tid":2141839,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣獨立開發遊戲《赤毒 Red Virus》上架Steam和Itch.Io","createTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T16:08:24.000Z","uid":34676,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"48f0b97c8970079649f2c67a81d81e15537c9aab","tid":2141839,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z7-V0FyylOQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ7-V0FyylOQ&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2Bm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=b45fabb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z7-V0FyylOQ</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，這裡是台灣的獨立遊戲開發者Leonard H.，歷時數個月的開發，以赤病毒為主題的FPS遊戲《赤毒（Red Virus）》已在 Steam 頁面及 <a href=\"http://Itch.Io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FItch.Io&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F%2Bm6EOSy25kVi46SvbSXLY8%3D&h=5ca4f935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Itch.Io</a> 搶先發售（Early Access），在8月4日正式上市，希望大家會喜歡。遊戲目前提供了兩種模式，單人和多人模式，在多人模式中，玩家可開房組隊，支援4人連線破關。<br />\n <br />\n此遊戲只是想傳遞一個訊息，告知全世界赤毒的危害。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲故事背景設定於，2020年4月，世紀政府高官被毒王奴役，赤毒在各國爆發襲捲全世界，毒王和戰狼們擊破了人類最後的要塞-川牆，<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">無數中毒的NMSLese</span></strong></span>入侵自由世界，赤化了大地河流，將美國改造成NMSLand。<br />\n<br />\n為了拯救世界，玩家將扮演世界各國的英雄，共同合作滲透NMSLand，尋找赤毒的解藥。各國英雄擁有專屬的招式，如Mr.Wall將可以在遊戲中築牆抵禦病毒，<span class=\"red\">而TaiwanNo1則可用台灣國旗治療友方</span>。未來預期還會推出更多新地圖、英雄、模式和劇情。可以在這串參與開發提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n同時遊戲的所有資源（藝術素材，原始碼），以及遊戲製作教學，將逐步整理以Royalty-Free的方式釋出於本人的Fanbox，如有興趣的人可以前往訂閱贊助。<br />\n<br />\n本遊戲的官方社群媒體，正舉辦轉發分享抽64 Key活動，希望各位多多幫忙分享，感謝您。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89d3da1492eba90e0165af30dbf3eee76c190d6","tid":2141839,"uid":34676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"支支心又碎了"},{"pid":"0b8b1e78291fd26c4140993be40200893620d71e","tid":2141839,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85009ef263023d1910afb5431294867dd92b887f","tid":2141839,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"457f0463f9d5c93a3449aa090d0d9f846ed342fd","tid":2141839,"uid":314731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"係咪玩得啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d307bc186f5502b08a841ce9d2dc5a23605d3edf","tid":2141839,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"屌你條 trailer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9beba6e86fc12b3b86ade3014a2ddf2ab02ae3b7","tid":2141839,"uid":34676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d307bc186f5502b08a841ce9d2dc5a23605d3edf","tid":2141839,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"屌你條 trailer<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im